title: New: DIICE – Do Wrong
body:
With their debut track last year stirring up quite the fuss, UK duo **DIICE** are back with their second offering in the form of the equally as glossy Do Wrong.

Again merging elements of the likes of Marian Hill, Broods and Sylvan Esso – DIICE undoubtedly know their way around a punchy chorus. Check out Do Wrong below.
